videos.headline: J. Evans pass,to S. Rogers for 30 yds for a 1ST down
videos.description: Jerod Evans pass complete to Sam Rogers for 30 yds to the Tenn 32 for a 1ST down

videos.headline: Hokies strike first with passing touchdown
videos.description: Virginia Tech quarterback Jerod Evans throws a 7-yard touchdown to Sam Rogers to open up a 7-0 lead on No. 17 Tennessee.

videos.headline: McMillian takes it 69 yards to the house for Hokies
videos.description: Travon McMillian rushes 69 yards for a first-quarter touchdown to extend Virginia Tech's lead over Tennessee.

videos.headline: Va Tech Fumbles on their side of the field, giving Tennessee life.

videos.headline: Dobbs tosses 38-yard TD to tie up for the Vols
videos.description: Tennessee QB Joshua Dobbs throws a 38-yard pass to Josh Malone for a second-half touchdown against Virginia Tech.

videos.headline: Watch Jalen Hurd take a vicious hit on the end of this 18 yard run

videos.headline: Dobbs takes it in himself to extend Vols' lead
videos.description: Tennessee quarterback Joshua Dobbs rushes for a 5-yard touchdown and the Vols extend their lead over Virginia Tech.

videos.headline: Dobbs fuels Vols past Hokies in Bristol
videos.description: Joshua Dobbs throws for three touchdowns and runs for two, combining for 197 yards in Tennessee's 45-24 win over Virginia Tech at Bristol Motor Speedway.

videos.headline: Tennessee takes checkered in Bristol
videos.description: In an epic matchup at Bristol Motor Speedway, Joshua Dobbs takes off for five touchdowns and Tennessee pulls away for a 45-24 win over Virginia Tech.
